About Woodhaven
mylane
2023-10-30T10:39:28-07:00
Woodhaven Estates offers the most home for your dollar and the leisure lifestyle of sunny central Florida.
Welcome to Woodhaven Estates, located in the lake-studded, citrus area of central Florida; just off Highway 27 in Sebring, where you will find all the amenities of big city living in the comfort of a small town setting away from heavy traffic and congestion. Woodhaven Estates is conveniently located within five minutes of shopping, restaurants, churches, and several medical centers. Beautiful lakes, state parks, and golf courses are located throughout Highlands County. Woodhaven Estates’ central location within the state puts any activity you desire within reach. Within a 2-hour drive or less, you can reach either of Florida’s east and west coast beaches along with most major theme parks, including Disney World, Sea World, Universal, and Busch Gardens.
Family owned and operated for more than 3 decades with great care, this 55+ community is pleased to offer “Your key to leisure living” without breaking the bank.
Woodhaven Estates provides great value with upscale amenities. Whether it is lounging in our heated pool, getting together for a competitive game of billiards, shuffleboard, bocce, or cards; or just meeting friends for a meal at the clubhouse; the list of resident activities is endless. Enjoy wide, paved, well-lit streets within the park. All home porches are reinforced for enhanced wind protection. Trash pickup and the use of all amenities are included. Cable TV, underground utilities, central sewage, and city water add to the ease of leisure living.
So whether you like to roam or stay close to home, Woodhaven Estates offers the most home for your dollar and the leisure lifestyle of sunny central Florida.
